{"tid":881255,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解輕鐵咁臭","createTime":"2018-10-29T09:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T02:27:34.000Z","uid":71166,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"275aebc0f6dae615804dddf004db626c1d43d40c","tid":881255,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成陣臭忽 + 臭鞋屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4191c0cc8112f223dabe897af7a8b40bbe1a867c","tid":881255,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:52:00.000Z","msg":"臭屎忽味"},{"pid":"714488c5894a4dce0447a05bb110f04aa3190180","tid":881255,"uid":200595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"又污糟"},{"pid":"97b79d96ba16d6f159d636f7293d80de062de270","tid":881255,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"714488c5894a4dce0447a05bb110f04aa3190180","tid":881255,"uid":200595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"又污糟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"真係痴線"},{"pid":"f60225aa45101427d71fd449cb5a53c857529beb","tid":881255,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:26:21.000Z","msg":"多支那人"},{"pid":"f5f1db9491ee163a23b7de82925eea91747f9fbc","tid":881255,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"冷氣機臭味洗極無用？　浸大首證人體皮屑是異味根源 (15:46)<br />\n（楊柏賢攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180131/s00001/ef799997bb07fbcf1858e27c95bb4098.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180131%2Fs00001%2Fef799997bb07fbcf1858e27c95bb4098.jpg&h=08d20008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖3之1 - （楊柏賢攝）<br />\n<br />\n冷氣機傳出臭味，洗極都無用，異味來源可能與你我身體有關！浸大公布一項研究成果，首次證實人體皮屑如頭皮、手皮、腳皮等，可以成為冷氣製冷系統的細菌食物來源，令冷氣噴出怪味似腳臭、口臭，以至是小便味。<br />\n<br />\n浸會大學生物系副教授賴嘉雯表示，人體皮膚角質細胞每日老化，會產生死皮。皮屑含角質蛋白、脂質及脂肪酸等，吸進製冷系統後，內藏細菌可產生角質蛋白酵素將之分解，繼而經出風口傳播異味。<br />\n<br />\n研究從浸大10間冷氣傳出臭味的教職員辦公室進行實驗，從冷氣系統收集細菌樣本中，以葡萄球菌揮發性脂肪酸及角質蛋白酵素活性較高，前者會傳出體臭，後者較易傳出尿味。<br />\n<br />\n賴嘉雯表示，重複清洗冷氣非減輕異味長遠對策，治本之法是減少皮膚鱗屑進入冷氣系統，例如安裝或更換密度合適的隔塵網，有些可阻隔10微米（0.001厘米）皮屑，效果最理想。"},{"pid":"0ba3dc99766b4eb14ba67ff1d434c42646282b0a","tid":881255,"uid":174164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"真心唔明點解咁尻臭, 個陣阿婆阿伯味再加上強國人個間臭味不得了<br />\n而家真係唔會搭輕鐵"},{"pid":"435d6571ff6697b946ac9e7e16acc45901d8e74b","tid":881255,"uid":10079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:09:58.000Z","msg":"多豬"},{"pid":"e903fdb9727fd61559c20075fef73bc222fd9bdb","tid":881255,"uid":67144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:23:59.000Z","msg":"因為啲死窮撚，有窮撚味"},{"pid":"bdd34f8bd3b81c5941d6c7918185f6c144c86c90","tid":881255,"uid":109655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:25:27.000Z","msg":"周地牛屎 個個踩完屎上車"},{"pid":"a62f2d868ff0123d3feff3e8532ba63a9c352944","tid":881255,"uid":377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"梗係啦，啲人帶豬帶雞帶牛上車，唔臭就有鬼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}